Use the input group component to accessibly define the labels used with inputs. All inputs require labels for usability and accessibility.

```jsx
<FormGroup>
          <FormLabel htmlFor="formInput">Label</FormLabel>
            <FormHint>Hint text</FormHint>
          <Input aria-describedby="formHint" width="20" id="formInput" name="test" />
        </FormGroup>
```
